



Shona / ʃoʊnə / [6] (chiShona) waa luqadda Bantu ee ugu ballaadhan oo ah luqad koowaad waxayna ku dhalataa Shona dadka Zimbabwe. Ereyga waxaa sidoo kale loo isticmaalaa in lagu garto dadka ka hadlaya mid ka mid ah noocyada Central Shona: Zezuru, Karanga, Manyika iyo Korekore. Marka la eego warbixinta Clement Doke ee 1931, Ururka Shona ama Standard Shona ayaa laga soo saaray noocyada Central Shona. Sababtoo ah joogitaanka magaalada caasimadda ee gobolka Zezuru, noocyo kala duwan ayaa ku yimid inay ku taliyaan Standard Shona.
Qeybta ugu weyn ee luuqadaha la xidhiidha (oo loo yaqaan luqadaha Shona ee luuqadaha) sidoo kale waxaa ka mid ah Ndau (Eastern Shona) iyo Kalanga (Western Shona), laakiin kuwa ku hadla luqadahaas waxay door bidaan aqoonsigooda gaarka ah waxayna badiyaa diidaan wixii xiriir ah ee ereyada Shona.
